============================
  INSTALLASI XAMPP
============================

$ donwload xampp
$ cd /home/[username]/Downloads
$ sudo chmod 755 [package_name]
$ sudo ./[package_name]
$ ikutit perintah sampaia finish
$ start mysql & apache
$ http://localhost/phpmyadmin (in browser)

source : https://phoenixnap.com/kb/how-to-install-xampp-on-ubuntu

